/RC_williams_c37872f6-b5e6-4e9b-8239-f470d0f1c661.png?v=1742572451" alt="author photo of rc williams" class="r-gtkm2y" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="a1fe63b8-ba63-423f-bae4-866f895fd83b" class="r-q9ykoa"><div data-rid="d0ae9286-0e3c-49d7-a115-59196b1df7b8" class="r-zc4awu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>By: RC Williams (Founder, CEO)</p></span></div><div data-rid="64f3bd36-1b5e-4b5c-ba15-a74330aa3e3c" class="r-eev3rn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>April 1st, 2026</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="bdba4292-a783-4ee0-b365-dda586fbed75" class="r-nelah9"></div><div data-rid="d5908846-c487-4478-8ea3-ebe1d9c93f7d" class="r-yucdhw"><div data-rid="942dbd70-c0ad-42e3-b30c-3a76bcfb76b2" class="r-zca5qg"><div data-rid="cbc39ffe-f353-4c65-b0c8-117494b88749" class="r-1cgjk5k"><div data-rid="e88a1edf-bec1-4e3d-b90f-45e6d03db80e" class="r-14g63qy"><picture data-rid="74ce2d81-a048-4c29-99a6-2a4e48c04cf1" class="r-ojwopk"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/f9993471-10f2-4746-b3ea-3e582d9d55b4?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/f9993471-10f2-4746-b3ea-3e582d9d55b4?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/f9993471-10f2-4746-b3ea-3e582d9d55b4?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/f9993471-10f2-4746-b3ea-3e582d9d55b4" class="r-1879axv" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="6701b190-9140-4695-af8f-df0b986654b2" class="r-1bqyl92"><div data-rid="79ff7512-3152-4e2c-8dd8-fb8dc44d9d68" class="r-1ouahoa alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px"><span style="width:100%"><p>My Mom Wanted To Give Up On Sleep Forever</p></span></div><div data-rid="95d36d3e-80e4-4a6c-be27-16717752f5ba" class="r-adla8u"><div data-rid="7e008ed4-3a9c-4a14-81a4-14f5e3dcfd65" class="r-14orkd8 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Not figuratively. She literally told me, "I think this is just my life now." She was in her 50s, wandering the house at 2 and 3 in the morning, exhausted every single day, and completely out of options. That conversation broke my heart — and it's the reason Rejuvia exists.</p><p><br></p><p>If you just watched me tell this story in the video that brought you here, I want to go deeper.</p><p><br></p><p>Because the full story matters. And if you're anything like my mom — if you've tried everything and nothing has worked — what I'm about to share might change the way you sleep for the rest of your life.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="e15dfb9c-1762-44c4-81cb-e97129941800" class="r-1hsq5w0"><div data-rid="9dec94da-ae4b-4d5a-b67f-1b528d9a9a97" class="r-s3mvqs"><div data-rid="27a78e5e-bd84-4e36-a1d2-575cd6736382" class="r-5tpysh alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px"><span style="width:100%"><p>My Mom Tried Everything To Sleep. Nothing Worked.</p></span></div><div data-rid="a714b983-3e78-44ec-b43d-a4aeabd8fabb" class="r-b3pw1g"><div data-rid="ca6d67e6-7f89-498b-94bf-48d97309aa5f" class="r-12xe6g0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>My mom did everything right. She went to her doctor. She followed the advice. She tried hard sleeping pills — the kind your doctor prescribes when nothing else works. She tried over-the-counter sleep aids, high-dose melatonin gummies, magnesium powders, and chamomile teas.</p><br><p>Some of it would knock her out. But she'd wake up at 2 AM feeling like an 18-wheeler hit her. Groggy. Foggy. Worse than before she went to bed. And the next morning? She'd drag herself through the day like a zombie, only to do it all over again that night.</p><br><p>The sleep issues weren't just about falling asleep — they were about staying asleep. Between menopause, the stress of running a household, and the mental calendar that never shuts off, her brain simply would not let her rest.</p><br><p>I watched this happen from the time I was 16 years old. By the time I left for college, I knew I had to do something about it.</p><br><p>I went to the University of Pennsylvania with one mission that had nothing to do with my degree: figure out why nothing on the market was working for women like my mom — and build something that actually did.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="7a24ea22-fb90-4e38-b811-8934b6d38308" class="r-1s3r9le"><div data-rid="e6b09f9d-4961-4472-a4a3-cbeaaea13ea3" class="r-1jhvrvm"><picture data-rid="dabfe8fd-fcc3-4ce0-bc37-04e58b79c876" tabindex="0" role="link" class="r-1ewjt7x"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/476e93f9-30dc-45b5-985a-aba204196726?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/476e93f9-30dc-45b5-985a-aba204196726?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/476e93f9-30dc-45b5-985a-aba204196726?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/476e93f9-30dc-45b5-985a-aba204196726" class="r-1xk741u" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="4cd9a754-73ba-4b29-88ad-2afca6ea0eb8" class="r-vmqqf3"><div data-rid="7b52616a-2b9a-4ca2-a8fe-e3b95e638880" class="r-1i0mn4u alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px"><span style="width:100%"><p>The Problem Was Never The Ingredients. It Was The Delivery System.</p></span></div><div data-rid="3a5cdc72-f6ae-4b30-b89f-4cc09badb473" class="r-b0qlw0"><div data-rid="83d777d1-c8ba-42be-9071-a5e088b73901" class="r-1najhl2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Here's what I found after years of research that changed everything:</p><br><p><strong>The pills and gummies my mom was taking weren't failing because of what was in them. They were failing because of how her body absorbed them.</strong></p><br><p>Think about it. You swallow a sleeping pill at 9 PM. It drops into your stomach. Your digestive system has to break it down — a process that takes 60 to 90 minutes. Along the way, your liver filters out roughly half the active ingredients before they ever reach your bloodstream.</p><br><p>So by the time that pill actually "kicks in," it's 10:00 or 10:30 at night. It's half as potent as what you swallowed. And because manufacturers know this, they overload the dose — cramming in 10 to 12 milligrams of melatonin to compensate for what your body will waste.</p><br><p>That's why you feel drugged in the morning. The excess ingredients linger in your system for hours after you wake up. You're not rested. You're sedated. And there's a massive difference.</p><br><p>Once I understood this, the solution became obvious.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="305bade0-dbe8-46c1-8b7a-f7a176daac34" class="r-5qm40h"><div data-rid="d173d519-232a-416c-a25a-43166a570ab4" class="r-12k0m3q"><div data-rid="db18d5b2-306a-49c5-a994-5e58a6280153" class="r-habiy5 alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px"><span style="width:100%"><p>So I Spent 4 Years at Penn Building Something Different</p></span></div><div data-rid="4cf71e50-c20b-4f29-95e2-1954a81570bb" class="r-15ia9c"><div data-rid="b7f40d53-4906-4ff2-b5fa-33ddc2133bc9" class="r-8cmeo5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Instead of another pill or gummy that has to survive your digestive system, I created the first oral sleep spray designed to bypass it entirely.</p><br><p>You spray it under your tongue. It absorbs directly into your bloodstream in minutes. No digestion. No waiting. No wasted ingredients.</p><br><p>This is called sublingual absorption — and it's the same delivery method used in emergency medicine when speed matters. Your body absorbs up to 60% more of the active compounds compared to swallowing a pill. That's not marketing. That's biology.</p><br><p>We formulated it with 13 of the best all-natural sleep ingredients on the planet. To calm racing thoughts: Passionflower, GABA, L-Theanine, and Chamomile. To help you fall asleep fast: Melatonin (2mg — not the 10-12mg overload you find in gummies) and 5-HTP. To keep you asleep through the night: Valerian Root, Hops Flower Head, Magnolia, and Lemon Balm. And to support next-day clarity: Magnesium, Organic Feverfew Leaf, and Peppermint Leaf.</p><br><p>Every ingredient is precisely dosed. Every batch is triple lab-tested. No fillers, no artificial dyes, no junk. </p><br><p>Just clean ingredients that actually work — delivered the way your body was designed to absorb them.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="29309f5d-7eac-4b89-be32-a89ec488849e" class="r-ubtjx4"><div data-rid="d06a4b1e-c8a6-490a-be3e-c117c6393431" class="r-7qq2sa"><picture data-rid="14465cd9-0da8-429f-8cb5-54a027036d80" class="r-301pqx"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/e58f14cc-f6b7-4b4e-b8a6-74b308589d6d?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/e58f14cc-f6b7-4b4e-b8a6-74b308589d6d?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/e58f14cc-f6b7-4b4e-b8a6-74b308589d6d?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/e58f14cc-f6b7-4b4e-b8a6-74b308589d6d" class="r-14fsvul" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="411d90e9-6f0b-487a-a429-e41e8ed6bb6a" class="r-eba16"><div data-rid="8df5be2d-24e7-4a66-843a-e70ef078f890" class="r-gr0xcx alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px"><span style="width:100%"><p>My Mom Was The First Person To Try It. Here's What Happened.</p></span></div><div data-rid="83690c80-aba1-4c48-834b-709ba5617366" class="r-1eyyuhk"><div data-rid="3e8ecc8e-78e6-431a-b653-80cfcb5efcc1" class="r-1wui2qj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The first night she used it, she sprayed it under her tongue, set it on her nightstand, and was asleep in 15 minutes. She didn't wake up at 2 AM. She didn't pace the house. She slept through the entire night — for the first time in years.</p><br><p>When she woke up the next morning, she called me and said something I'll never forget: "I feel like myself again."</p><br><p>No grogginess. No hangover. No fog. Just rested. Like she used to feel before sleep became a battle.</p><p>She's been using Rejuvia for years now. And here's the part that surprises people: she doesn't need it every night anymore. She wanted something that worked when she needed it — without becoming dependent on it. </p><br><p>That's exactly what we built. No tolerance buildup. No dependency. You stay in control.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="b5cf40ef-659e-40a3-8914-4057f9fb06b4" class="r-5dst8y"><div data-rid="7f50de66-d179-4b30-9d70-7e4a738545ed" class="r-kmqcge"><div data-rid="542df6bd-6539-4ab2-bc46-b8ee2dcfbfc8" class="r-1x7rf68 alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px"><span style="width:100%"><p>We Never Planned to Build a Business. We Just Wanted to Help My Mom.</p></span></div><div data-rid="67965dc4-0b32-4206-90ff-4fa32495e75a" class="r-15emi2z"><div data-rid="2a14be04-b6f9-4284-94cf-e8d160435002" class="r-2j0377 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>But word got out. My mom told her friends. They told their friends. A few doctors tried it and started recommending it to patients. And suddenly, this thing I built in a dorm room for one person was helping thousands.</p><p><br></p><p>Today, over 300,000 people across the country use Rejuvia every single night. More than 500 doctors recommend it — and use it themselves. We've earned over 6,000 five-star reviews and been featured in Forbes, Healthline, Women's Health, Bustle, and Scary Mommy.</p><p><br></p><p>But it's still a family business. My mom and I still do customer service. If you email us, there's a real chance one of us will reply.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="25589dea-220c-4a69-8b6a-580d0700bdaf" class="r-m54ouq"><div data-rid="051cc616-ea57-4247-a705-415086e42be4" class="r-4boqxe"><picture data-rid="38281605-c0a6-4257-b592-d0f5a54952dd" class="r-4w2dkc"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/007625be-7a3f-4575-b765-8f6ba59838ff?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/007625be-7a3f-4575-b765-8f6ba59838ff?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/007625be-7a3f-4575-b765-8f6ba59838ff?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/007625be-7a3f-4575-b765-8f6ba59838ff" class="r-nysz1m" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="74bc62b5-71bf-499e-93a9-667684fdc5f5" class="r-1m5avdd"><div data-rid="21d6f968-c685-48bb-9c5b-6712c163130f" class="r-35wjz8 alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--re